 the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#MH\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cw part=\"I\">Ἀρτεμιδ\u003C/w>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>Ψ\u003Cunclear>υχ\u003C/unclear> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#MH\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text according to Kaibel in IG\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"line 1\">\n                        \u003Cnote>Kaibel suggests: Ἀρτεμιδ[ώ]ρο[υ], after Gualtherus\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The fragment was reported first in the second edition of Gualtherus' corpus, where it was transcribed in Latin letters. As a result, it was included also by Mommsen in CIL (no.7466) and the doublet does not seem to have been noticed by either Mommsen or Kaibel.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                    \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus